args: Listen up! It's too dark to keep going,\nso we're going to make camp here!
We should be able to make it back to the\ncastle tomorrow, so stay positive!
Today's show was really something,\nAnnelie. You did great!
Aw, you're too nice to me.
Hey, and thanks for tagging around with\nus as we make the rounds.
Don't worry about it. Honestly, it gives me\na chance to see what the Empire is up to.
Someone might be under attack. Come on!
Yes, thanks to yo—Hold a moment!\nYou're the traitorous prince!
And you look to be an imperial soldier.
The last one you'll ever see, dog!
Please, you have to stop. You're so\nwounded, you can barely hold your\nsword out in front of you.
We'll let you return to your unit,\nbut we need to tend to your wounds first.
I need no pity from my enemies!
But the prince is right: Staying out here\nalone and injured is a good way to end\nup as some fiend's plaything.
Come on. We'll keep you safe.
Damn it... How did it come to this?
How did a simple scouting mission end up\nwith me receiving medical treatment from\nthe army of our greatest enemy?!
Do you want to see a circus show, friend?
What?! Oh, you're that little girl who was\nwith the prince earlier.
Sure am, chum! Oh, and my name's\nAnnelie, not ＂little girl.＂ So then!\nWhat do you say about that show?
Ha! What reason could I possibly have\nto accept such an absurd offer?!
It's humiliating enough being treated by\nyou lot without seeing you gambol and\ncaper about in front of me!
Look, I know times are tough right now,\nbut that's when you need a circus most!
C'mon, it's gonna cheer you up.\nI proooomise...
Like hell it will! Are you MAD?!
You DO know the Empire is cracking down\non circuses and the like, yes?!
Oh, yeah, I heard all about that. \nBut you just look so darn gloomy,\nI can't help but wanna cheer you up!
The circus exists to make everyone happy.
And imperial soldiers still count as\n＂everyone＂ last time I checked.
Why don't you give it a try?\nHer shows really are fun.
Prepare for a magical, mystical,\nMARVELOUS circus unlike anything\nyou've ever seen before!
Forget your worldly cares and let us\nwelcome you to a world of dreams!
Bah! What a bunch of pablum!\nI'm a man of the glorious Empire,\nnot some twee villager who... Hmm?
Yep! Consider them as a little memento\nof our show today.
Like I said before, it doesn't matter\nwho you are or where you're from...
If you're watching one of our shows,\nyou're a valued guest like anyone else.
For the final spectacle this evening,\nLiger will leap through a ring of fire!
Let's make this a show to remember!
Thank you so much for watching!
Bravo! Bravo! I've never seen such a...\nEr, I mean...
Uh oh. Looks like SOMEONE had fun\ndespite trying so hard to be a glum chum.
See? The circus isn't so bad.
Well, I...suppose it has a certain charm.
But surely you don't mean to let me go?
If your injuries are healed, we have no\nreason to detain you further.
Very well—but this changes nothing!\nWhen next we meet, things will go\nvery differently, I assure you!
Byeee! Have a safe trip baaaack!
He seemed to enjoy that in spite of his\nbest efforts—and that's what counts.
It sure is! And yeah, he's just one soldier,\nso that's just a tiny step in the grand\nscheme of things...

But I think it's the first ripple in a wave
that's going to change everything—
and as long as I don't give up,
it's only going to get bigger!
And if you've learned anything about me,\nit's that I NEVER give up!
Not until every last person is happy!
Thanks for always believing in me,\n{player_name}!
Gya! ...Er, I thought you were saving the\nkiss until after your dream came true?
And I was doing SO well with that, too!
Oh well! Maybe just think of this as a little\ntreat for getting me one step closer.
